title: Policy6141.32(6)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

<ol type="A">
<li>It is recognized that technology is changing rapidly and that advances in the area of telecommunications will necessitate future modification of guidelines. The district will look to the District Technology Task Force for regular review of procedures and for recommendations which will keep guidelines current with both technological and curricular developments.</li>
</ol>
